                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "3ca7cd6a2f584425be9b8",
                    "stepText": "Finally, using the conservation of momentum, calculate the final velocity $!$v_f$!$ of the combined system. Recall that the total initial momentum is the momentum of the debris (since the astronaut is stationary) and the combined mass is $!$m_A + m_D$!$. What is the final velocity?",
